   "source": "https://vocus.cc/article/634d62d5fd8978000135e75b",
   "readMin": 5,
   "body": "<p>萬聖節手紙偶教學來囉！用最簡單的材料，加上一點想像力，變成拿在手中會動的紙偶，可愛又嚇人～</p><h2>⭐ 觀看影片</h2><a class=\"ytlink\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8tFM1ukUDhc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/8tFM1ukUDhc/hqdefault.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"觀看 YouTube 影片\"><span class=\"ytplay\">▶ 在 YouTube 觀看影片</span></a><p><br></p><h2>材料</h2><p>A4白紙、雙面膠帶、剪刀、鉛筆、水彩筆、顏料</p><h2>步驟</h2><p>先把紙張直向對折一半</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/a0b4e835-e9b4-4eb2-a1aa-b037184567c1.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>兩邊再各自反方向對折一半</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/74ac3ed7-a776-4079-9d4d-54c935b784e2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><figure><img src=\"assets/images/fb74499f-c693-484c-ab0f-83e76f9ec6f9.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>外層用鉛筆畫出鬼的圖案</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/ce8aeba5-9901-4e61-bb0f-63692fac4e03.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>把紙打開畫中間的部分</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/89df7f40-5c7a-424f-bd6b-e9817fbe459c.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>塗上顏色、描輪廓</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/f899085d-820c-4ada-b64b-41df1bf57ea7.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>剪下來</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/15227cfd-8653-40b6-9d57-bf0b63eb4a96.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>背面黏上多餘的紙條做成把手</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/d5aba660-bbf0-4b9e-8595-c58895548e48.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>變成可愛的萬聖節手偶啦！</p><figure><img src=\"assets/images/24c6140b-80cf-46bc-bc65-619c5f86f606.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"></figure>"
